            <div type="edition">
            <ab>
                <lb n="1"/>Diis <expan><abbr>Ma</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan>.
                <lb n="2"/>
                    <persName>
                        <name key="Mystes">Mysti</name>
                    </persName>
                    <persName>
                        <name type="praenomen" key="Lucius"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan></name>
                        <name type="gentilicium" key="Volusius">Volusi</name>
                <lb n="3"/>
                        <name type="cognomen" key="Saturninus">Saturnini</name>
                    </persName> <expan><abbr>ser</abbr><ex>vo</ex></expan>
                <lb n="4"/>
                    <persName>
                        <name type="gentilicium" key="Volusia">Volusia</name>
                        <name type="cognomen" key="Irene">Irene</name>
                    </persName> et
                <lb n="5"/>
                    <persName>
                        <name key="Dorius">Dorio</name>
                    </persName> filio
                <lb n="6"/>vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan> <num value="15">XV</num>, <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensibus</ex></expan> <num value="6">VI</num>.
                <lb n="7"/>permissu
                    <persName>
                        <name type="praenomen" key="Quintus"><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan></name>
                    </persName> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan>.
            </ab></div>
            
            <div type="translation">
                <p>To the divine spirits. Volusia Irene (made this) for Mystes, slave of Lucius Volusius Saturninus, and to son Dorius, (who) lived fifteen years and six months. (Done) by permission of our Quintus.</p></div>

